1.5. The owner of the ad is responsible for the information contained in the ad.

1.6. The site is not responsible for transactions made by users.

1.7. Ads that do not comply with these rules can at any time be removed or edited by the site administration without the permission and notification of the author of the ad.

1.8. Comments to announcements and articles that do not comply with these rules and the Law of the Republic of Uzbekistan "On the Mass Media" can at any time be removed or edited by the site administration without the permission and notification of the author of the announcement.


1.9. The user agrees that theredder.uz/ The Site Administration, if necessary, has the right to make calls to him (her), with a record of such a conversation, in the following cases:

- receipt of a complaint from another user about a violation of the Rules and / or User Agreement;

