1.10. Such a call, as well as its recording, is carried out only for internal use, in order to eliminate violations of the Rules and / or the User Agreement, as well as as confirmation of the information provided by the user during a telephone conversation (for example, when the user requests a recording of such a conversation). theredder.uz/ The site does not pursue the goal of distributing or publishing audio recordings to third parties. The conversation is recorded exclusively for the above purposes.


Article 2. Subject of ads prohibited from publication on the site
