 Пользователь имеет право прекратить доступ к своему Личному кабинету без возможности восстановления такого доступа. В этом случае Пользователь не вправе осуществлять повторную Регистрацию в том числе, с использованием в составе Учетных данных указанного Пользователем ранее на Redder.uz адреса электронной почты.





Privacy policy and protection of personal information

Providing information by the client:

When registering and submitting ads on the site, the client provides the following information: name, e-mail address, phone number (the client's computer IP address is recorded automatically). The client, when registering on the site, his contact information (name, email address, phone number), understands that the data entered by him is not personal data, provided to the company voluntarily and in the amount necessary and sufficient for the company to fulfill its obligations to the client.

Non-disclosure of information received by the company:

We use the personalized information of a specific visitor to the site solely to provide him with high-quality services and their accounting. We do not disclose the personalized data of some site visitors URL to other site visitors. We never publish personalized information in the public domain and do not transfer it to third parties. The only exceptions are situations when the provision of such information to authorized state bodies is prescribed by the current legislation of the Republic of Uzbekistan. We only publish and distribute reports based on the collected anonymous data. At the same time, the reports do not contain information by which it would be possible to identify the personalized data of service users. We also use anonymous data for internal analysis, the purpose of which is to develop the products and services of the URL.

It is not considered a violation of the provision of information by the company to agents and third parties acting on the basis of an agreement with the company to fulfill obligations to the client.

It is not considered a violation of obligations to disclose information in accordance with reasonable and applicable legal requirements.

The company is not responsible for the information provided by the client on the site in a public form.

Links:

The site www.theredder.uz may contain links to other sites that are not related to our company and owned by third parties. We are not responsible for the accuracy, completeness and reliability of the information posted on third-party sites, and we do not undertake any obligation to maintain the confidentiality of the information you leave on such sites.

Limitation of Liability:

We do our best to comply with this privacy policy, however, we cannot guarantee the safety of information in the event of exposure to factors beyond our control, the result of which will be the disclosure of information. The site www.theredder.uz and all information posted on it are presented on an "as is" basis without any guarantees. We are not responsible for adverse consequences, as well as for any losses caused as a result of restricting access to the site URL or as a result of visiting the site and the use of information posted on it.

Mailings and information messages:

When registering on the site, the client agrees to receive advertising and informational mailings from the company (announcements of changes, notifications about important events, information about payment and actions with announcements, training materials, etc.).
The frequency of receiving advertising and informational mailings is no more than one message per day. The exception is service notices of action with announcements on the site. The opt-out option is provided in each message as a link.
Mailings are sent in the form of an e-mail to the address and / or a short message (SMS) to the phone number specified by the client during registration or posting an advertisement.


User Agreement Redder.uz

Information provided by Users.

By posting Announcements on Redder.uz, the User makes the Information specified in the Announcement publicly available and understands that the posted information is published on Redder.uz in the public domain, that is, it is available for review to any Redder.uz visitor (an unlimited number of persons) in all countries of the world where it is possible to use the Internet and access the site, respectively, the User understands and assumes all the risks associated with such placement of information, including, but not limited to: the risk of getting an email address into spam mailing lists; messages, the risk of getting an email address to various scammers, the risk of a phone number getting to SMS spammers and / or SMS scammers and other risks arising from such posting of information

Using the services of the Site, the User understands that:

 By specifying the data in the appropriate form on the Site, the User confirms that he provides his consent to the collection and processing of his personal data;

 Filling out various forms, including those with personal data, is carried out on his (her) initiative;

 The site collects data provided by the User solely for their temporary storage in accordance with the procedure established by the legislation of the Republic of Uzbekistan, for the purpose of subsequent transfer of such data to the bank, and does not use the specified data for any other purposes.


 User obligations
 The user undertakes to act exclusively in accordance with the current legislation and the User Agreement of Redder.uz, and also bear full responsibility in accordance with the legislation of the Republic of Uzbekistan for his own actions and inaction on Redder.uz and when using the Services.

 The User is prohibited from using the Services, as well as any information received on the Site for other purposes.

The user also undertakes:

not take any action that could lead to a disproportionate load on the Redder.uz infrastructure;
not copy, reproduce, modify, distribute or present to the public any information contained on Redder.uz (except for the Information provided by the User himself)
not to interfere with the work of Redder.uz, as well as not to interfere with the operation of automatic systems or processes, in order to block or restrict access to Redder.uz.


Warranties and liability

 The user is responsible for the actions taken on the Site in accordance with the current legislation of the Republic of Uzbekistan, including responsibility for the content of information posted by him and violation of the rights of third parties in relation to the Goods and / or information posted on the Site.

 The user is responsible for the offered in relation to the Goods and the transactions concluded in connection with them, for the choice of counterparties for the transaction and the consequences arising from the transaction. All transactions in relation to the Goods are concluded between the Users directly. Redder.uz is not a participant and / or intermediary of transactions made by Users based on the information received on Redder.uz, does not control and is not responsible for such transactions.

 Redder.uz is a tool that enables Users to post Ads in relation to Products, the sale and / or purchase of which is permitted by law and the User Agreement. At the same time, Redder.uz does not always check the Ads posted by Users. Thus, the quality, safety, legality and compliance of the Goods with its description, as well as the Seller's ability to sell and / or the Buyer to purchase the Goods are beyond the control of Redder.uz. In this connection, Redder.uz is not responsible for the content of the information provided by the Users, including the content of the Ads, the use by the Users of trademarks, logos of third parties and the terms of the Seller's offer.


Term of the User Agreement

 This User Agreement enters into force from the moment the User starts using the Redder.uz Services, regardless of the fact of the User's Registration or posting the Announcement on Redder.uz, and is valid indefinitely.

 The user has the right to terminate access to his Personal Account without the possibility of restoring such access. In this case, the User does not have the right to re-register, including using the email address specified by the User earlier on Redder.uz as part of the Credentials.






Maxfiylik siyosati va shaxsiy ma'lumotlarni himoya qilish

Mijoz tomonidan ma'lumotlarni taqdim etish:

Saytda reklamalarni ro'yxatdan o'tkazish va yuborishda mijoz quyidagi ma'lumotlarni taqdim etadi: ism, elektron pochta manzili, telefon raqami (mijozning kompyuter IP-manzili avtomatik tarzda yozib qo'yiladi). Mijoz, saytga ro'yxatdan o'tish paytida, uning aloqa ma'lumotlari (ism, elektron pochta manzili, telefon raqami), u kiritgan ma'lumotlar shaxsiy ma'lumot emasligini, kompaniyaga o'z ixtiyori bilan va kerakli miqdorda taqdim etilganligini tushunadi. kompaniya mijoz oldidagi majburiyatlarini bajarishi shart.

Kompaniya olgan ma'lumotlarni oshkor qilmaslik:

Biz ma'lum bir tashrif buyuruvchining shaxsiy ma'lumotlaridan faqat unga yuqori sifatli xizmatlar ko'rsatish va ularni hisobga olish uchun foydalanamiz. Biz ba'zi tashrif buyuruvchilarning shaxsiy ma'lumotlarini boshqa foydalanuvchilarga oshkor qilmaymiz. Biz hech qachon shaxsiy ma'lumotni jamoatchilikka e'lon qilmaymiz va uni uchinchi shaxslarga bermaymiz. Vakolatli davlat organlariga bunday ma'lumotlarni taqdim etish O'zbekiston Respublikasining amaldagi qonunchiligida belgilangan holatlar bundan mustasno. Biz faqat to'plangan anonim ma'lumotlarga asoslangan hisobotlarni nashr qilamiz va tarqatamiz. Shu bilan birga, hisobotlarda xizmat foydalanuvchilarining shaxsiy ma'lumotlarini aniqlash mumkin bo'lgan ma'lumotlar mavjud emas. Biz, shuningdek, ichki tahlil uchun anonim ma'lumotlardan foydalanamiz, ularning maqsadi - URL mahsulotlari va xizmatlarini ishlab chiqish.

Kompaniya mijozlar oldidagi majburiyatlarini bajarish uchun kompaniya bilan tuzilgan shartnoma asosida harakat qilayotgan agentlarga va uchinchi shaxslarga ma'lumot berish qonunbuzarlik hisoblanmaydi.

Ma'lumotni oqilona va amaldagi qonun talablariga muvofiq oshkor qilish majburiyatlari buzilgan deb hisoblanmaydi.

Kompaniya mijoz tomonidan saytda ochiq shaklda berilgan ma'lumot uchun javobgar emas.

Havolalar:

Www.theredder.uz saytida bizning kompaniyamizga aloqasi bo'lmagan va uchinchi shaxslarga tegishli bo'lgan boshqa saytlarga havolalar bo'lishi mumkin. Biz uchinchi tomon saytlarida joylashtirilgan ma'lumotlarning to'g'riligi, to'liqligi va ishonchliligi uchun javobgar emasmiz va siz bunday saytlarda qoldirgan ma'lumotlaringizning maxfiyligini saqlash majburiyatini o'z zimmamizga olmaymiz.

Mas'uliyatni cheklash:

Biz maxfiylik siyosatiga rioya qilish uchun qo'limizdan kelganini qilamiz, lekin biz nazorat qila olmaydigan omillar ta'sirida axborot xavfsizligiga kafolat bera olmaymiz, natijada ma'lumot oshkor bo'ladi. Www.theredder.uz sayti va unda joylashtirilgan barcha ma'lumotlar "hech qanday holatda" kafolatlanmagan holda taqdim etiladi. Biz salbiy oqibatlar, shuningdek, saytga kirishni cheklash natijasida etkazilgan zarar uchun javobgar emasmiz. URL yoki saytga tashrif buyurish va unda joylashtirilgan ma'lumotlardan foydalanish natijasida.

Pochta va axborot xabarlari:

Saytda ro'yxatdan o'tayotganda, mijoz kompaniyadan reklama va axborot jo'natmalarini olishga rozilik beradi (o'zgarishlar to'g'risida e'lonlar, muhim voqealar haqida xabarnomalar, to'lovlar to'g'risidagi ma'lumotlar va e'lonlar bilan harakatlar, o'quv materiallari va boshqalar).
Reklama va axborot jo'natmalarini qabul qilish chastotasi kuniga bir martadan oshmaydi. Istisno - bu saytdagi e'lonlari bo'lgan harakatlar to'g'risida bildirishnomalar. Qabul qilish varianti har bir xabarda havola sifatida berilgan.
Xatlar elektron pochta va / yoki mijoz tomonidan ko'rsatilgan telefon raqamiga qisqa xabar (SMS) shaklida, ro'yxatdan o'tish yoki reklama joylashtirish paytida yuboriladi.



Foydalanuvchi shartnomasi Redder.uz

Foydalanuvchilar tomonidan taqdim etilgan ma'lumotlar.

Redder.uz saytida E'lonlar joylashtirib, Foydalanuvchi E'londa ko'rsatilgan ma'lumotlarni hammaga ochiq qiladi va joylashtirilgan ma'lumot Redder.uz saytida hammaga ochiq bo'lganini, ya'ni Redder.uz saytining har bir tashrif buyuruvchisi ko'rib chiqishi uchun mavjudligini tushunadi. (cheklanmagan miqdordagi odamlar) Internetdan foydalanish va saytga kirish mumkin bo'lgan dunyoning barcha mamlakatlarida, foydalanuvchi ma'lumotni joylashtirish bilan bog'liq bo'lgan barcha xavflarni tushunadi va o'z zimmasiga oladi, shu jumladan: elektron pochta manzilini spam-jo'natmalar ro'yxatiga kiritish xavfi- turli xil firibgarlarga elektron pochta manzilini olish xavfi, SMS-spamerlarga va / yoki SMS-firibgarlarga telefon raqami tushish xavfi va bunday ma'lumotlarni joylashtirishdan kelib chiqadigan boshqa xavflar.

Sayt xizmatlaridan foydalangan holda, foydalanuvchi tushunadi:

 Saytda tegishli shaklda ma'lumotlarni ko'rsatib, Foydalanuvchi shaxsiy ma'lumotlarini yig'ish va qayta ishlashga roziligini berganligini tasdiqlaydi;

 Har xil shakllarni, shu jumladan shaxsiy ma'lumotlarga ega bo'lgan shakllarni to'ldirish uning tashabbusi bilan amalga oshiriladi;

 Sayt Foydalanuvchi tomonidan taqdim etilgan ma'lumotlarni faqat O'zbekiston Respublikasi qonunchiligida belgilangan tartibda vaqtincha saqlash uchun to'playdi, keyinchalik bunday ma'lumotlarni bankka o'tkazish maqsadida va ko'rsatilgan ma'lumotlardan hech kim uchun foydalanmaydi. boshqa maqsadlar.


 Foydalanuvchi majburiyatlari
 Foydalanuvchi faqat amaldagi qonun hujjatlariga va Redder.uz Foydalanuvchi shartnomasiga muvofiq harakat qilish majburiyatini oladi, shuningdek, Redder.uz saytidagi o'z xatti -harakatlari va harakatsizligi uchun va undan foydalanganda O'zbekiston Respublikasi qonun hujjatlariga muvofiq to'liq javobgar bo'ladi. Xizmatlar.

 Foydalanuvchiga Xizmatlardan, shuningdek Saytda olingan har qanday ma'lumotdan boshqa maqsadlarda foydalanish taqiqlanadi.

Shuningdek, foydalanuvchi quyidagilarni o'z zimmasiga oladi:

Redder.uz infratuzilmasiga nomutanosib yuklashga olib kelishi mumkin bo'lgan hech qanday chora ko'rmaslik;
Redder.uz saytida mavjud bo'lgan ma'lumotlardan nusxa ko'chirmang, ko'paytirmang, o'zgartirmang, tarqatmang yoki ommaga taqdim qilmang (Foydalanuvchining o'zi bergan ma'lumotlardan tashqari).
Redder.uz saytiga kirishni blokirovka qilish yoki cheklash maqsadida Redder.uz ishiga, shuningdek avtomatik tizimlar yoki jarayonlarning ishlashiga aralashmaslik.


Kafolat va javobgarlik

 Foydalanuvchi O'zbekiston Respublikasining amaldagi qonunchiligiga binoan Saytda qilingan harakatlar uchun, shu jumladan u joylashtirgan ma'lumotlarning mazmuni va Tovarlar va / yoki ma'lumotlarga nisbatan uchinchi shaxslarning huquqlarining buzilishi uchun javobgardir.

 Foydalanuvchi taklif qilingan Tovarlar va ular bilan bog'liq tuzilgan bitimlar, bitim uchun kontragentlarni tanlash va bitimdan kelib chiqadigan oqibatlar uchun javobgardir. Tovarlar bilan bog'liq barcha bitimlar to'g'ridan -to'g'ri Foydalanuvchilar o'rtasida tuziladi. Redder.uz Foydalanuvchilar tomonidan Redder.uz saytida olingan ma'lumotlarga asoslanib tuzilgan bitimlarning ishtirokchisi va / yoki vositachisi emas, bunday bitimlarni nazorat qilmaydi va javobgar emas.

 Redder.uz - bu foydalanuvchilarga sotish va / yoki sotib olish qonun va Foydalanuvchi shartnomasi bilan ruxsat berilgan mahsulotlarga nisbatan reklama joylashtirish imkoniyatini beradigan vosita. Shu bilan birga, Redder.uz har doim ham foydalanuvchilar tomonidan e'lon qilingan reklamalarni tekshirib ko'rmaydi. Shunday qilib, Tovarning sifati, xavfsizligi, qonuniyligi va uning tavsifiga muvofiqligi, shuningdek, Sotuvchining Tovarlarni sotish va / yoki Xarid qilish qobiliyati Redder.uz tomonidan nazorat qilinmaydi. Shu munosabat bilan, Redder.uz Foydalanuvchilar tomonidan taqdim etilgan ma'lumotlarning mazmuni, shu jumladan E'lonlarning mazmuni, Foydalanuvchilarning savdo belgilaridan foydalanishi, uchinchi shaxslarning logotiplari va Sotuvchining taklif shartlari uchun javobgar emas.


Foydalanuvchi shartnomasining amal qilish muddati

 Foydalanuvchi Shartnomasi, Foydalanuvchi ro'yxatdan o'tganligi yoki Redder.uz saytida E'lonni joylashidan qat'i nazar, Redder.uz xizmatlaridan foydalana boshlagan paytdan boshlab kuchga kiradi va muddatsiz amal qiladi.

 Foydalanuvchi shaxsiy hisobiga kirishni qayta tiklash imkoniyatisiz to'xtatishga haqli. Bunday holda, Foydalanuvchi qayta ro'yxatdan o'tishga haqli emas, shu jumladan Foydalanuvchi tomonidan ilgari Redder.uz saytida ko'rsatilgan elektron pochta manzilidan Ishonch ma'lumotlari tarkibida foydalanish.
